{"type":"FlowTopic","triggers":[{"type":"Trigger","name":"6dc0daea994b4c0d8bdf641b01c896f4","triggerType":"request","applicability":{"type":"Applicability","mode":"script","value":"true"},"id":"6dc0daea994b4c0d8bdf641b01c896f4"}],"goals":[{"name":"primary","trigger_id":"6dc0daea994b4c0d8bdf641b01c896f4","nodes":[{"type":"StartGoal","goal_id":"primary","greeting_msg":{"type":"String","mode":"string","value":""},"id":"1821b76dae664951984624918a8f2bef","name":"Start","expert_mode":false},{"type":"TerminateGoal","goal_id":"primary","confirmation_msg":{"type":"String","mode":"string","value":""},"id":"b4df58eeb84749dfa3737fac3bca85ff","name":"End","expert_mode":false},{"type":"ScriptedAction","script":"(function execute() {

    var notificationContext = JSON.parse(vaVars.global_notification_context);
    vaVars.auto_resolution_context_id = notificationContext.tableSysId;
    vaVars.action_sys_id = notificationContext.actionId;
    interactionId = vaSystem.getInteractionSysId();

    var contextHelper = new global.AutoResolutionContextHelper();
    var context = contextHelper.getContextDetails(vaVars.auto_resolution_context_id);
    contextHelper.setInteraction(vaVars.auto_resolution_context_id, interactionId);
    new global.AutoResolutionTaskHelper().associateTaskToInteraction(context.taskTable, context.taskId, interactionId);

    vaVars.topic_id = context.topicId;
    vaVars.task_id = context.taskId;
    vaVars.task_table = context.taskTable;
    vaVars.is_valid = context.isValid;
    vaVars.validation_reason = context.validationReason;
    vaVars.is_notification_expired = context.validationReason == 'Notification expired';
    vaVars.is_notification_accepted = context.validationReason == 'Notification accepted';

    var logUtils = new global.AutoResolutionLoggingUtils()
                        .withName('topic')
                        .withContextId(vaVars.auto_resolution_context_id)
                        .withTaskValues(vaVars.task_id, vaVars.task_table)
                        .withLanguage(context.language)
                        .withConfiguration(context.configId)
                        .withTopic(vaVars.topic_id);
    vaVars.loggingContext = JSON.stringify(logUtils.CONTEXT);
    var logger = logUtils.createLogger();
    logger.info('Starting Auto-Resoluton Topic');

     //!!!!!IMPORTANT: DO NOT CHANGE THIS VALUE!!!!!
    vaVars.is_iar_wrapper_topic = true;
})()
